  "text": "Please note that K and E are invariants of the incompressible Euler problem, i.e. of (1) with ν = 0. Following [CITATION_1] , we consider critical (i.e. stationary) points of E on level sets of K; that is, crit {E(ω) : K(ω) = γ; with mixed BCs (7); γ > 0 fixed}.",
